data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath step in ranch home. Sit on the covered front porch and relax. Inside you will discover lovely hardwood floors. Nice living room, dining room and kitchen complete with an island for added countertop space. The master bedroom has been enlarged and a sitting room was added as well as double closets. The main bathroom has also been updated. There is an additional bedroom on the main floor. Downstairs you will find a partially finished family room and utility room. There are also 2 bedrooms that have recently been added and  another full bathroom. Outside is a level back yard with a pool and patio,  complete with a pergola for all of your entertaining needs. The oversized garage provides plenty of storage and there are additional off-street parking spots.
